    onrelease CDATA #IMPLIED
    onhold CDATA #IMPLIED
    id CDATA #IMPLIED
>

<!-- Container: Blink - exactly one child widget with blinking animation -->
<!ELEMENT blink (collection | column | row | panel | blink | text | input | image | keyboard)>
<!ATTLIST blink
